{"tid":402441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堪輿學家：海洋公園應做法事請鬼魂離開","createTime":"2017-09-16T12:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T12:02:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":40,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"36fb8c3659acf53f40cedee2b1fce99bbd7d785c","tid":402441,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"堪輿學家區仲德博士表示，雖然農曆7月15日「鬼節」結束不久，但農曆7月未過，有部分鬼魂可能未返回「鬼門關」。鬼魂會依附陰森地方，在風水學上稱為「呼形喝象」，如墓穴、棺材等是最陰靈喜歡住居的地方。人們去「鬼屋」玩樂，即是騷擾鬼魂，當鬼魂不高興，產生報復心，找東西扑人。他續指事主21歲，有可能屬鼠，而今年是雞年，屬鼠、雞、狗、兔及馬都是犯太歲，流年不利。這些生肖的人，最好不要接觸棺材，亦不要去陰森的地方，盡量去陽氣重的地方比較安全。人們亦可以佛牌、觀音、太歲符護身。<br />\n<br />\n區解釋，農曆7月完結後，鬼魂便返回鬼門關。他建議樂園請高僧、道士在現場做法事超渡，請鬼魂離開，平息怒氣。"},{"pid":"e4d03ad7a6725d00d067d1ca45b423f1c1efeeb2","tid":402441,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cea01fe6057696f266b46dcf3d9da593187cb8","tid":402441,"uid":61325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"走左去黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbae73db0f35d2f7c6808807022a0fcfaa3e67d","tid":402441,"uid":93137,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"三七一開 乾坤一轉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe80b8df036b9f1de441b47f4c3dca6f28e2c65b","tid":402441,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"叫龍哥幫拖la"},{"pid":"372e92b46fe80842f1232bfff2f55595d16654ab","tid":402441,"uid":7699,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"re